author: Stadium
title: Has the NFL Stretched Itself Too Far?
text:
Bulletin and Review, 1410 Broadway Denison, IA 51442
Once again the NFL didn't put its best foot forward with its latest International Game in Week Six as the New York Jets and Denver Broncos "battled" to a 13-11 Denver victory.
As the NFL continues to expand internationally, it also tries to make sure the international playing surfaces meet league standards. That's where Nick Pappas comes in.
